{/* Intro Section */}

We’ve been there.

PeerFund was built out of real moments — the kind where you find yourself stretching every dollar… skipping a meal, selling your couch, or pushing rent back again. We know that cycle. We’ve lived it.

Our mission is to break that cycle by connecting people to each other — not to payday lenders. Whether you’re in need or you’re able to help, PeerFund lets you lend or borrow with transparency, trust, and community in mind.

{/* How It Works Section */}

How it works

  • Request a Loan: Simple form to ask for what you need, why you need it, and how long you need it for.
  • Get Matched: Lenders from the community can offer terms — you choose the one that works for you.
  • Repay Over Time: No hidden fees. No algorithms. Just transparent repayment with real humans.
